#: ../../talk/messages.rst:3
msgid "Interacting with messages"
msgstr "Idirghníomhú le teachtaireachtaí"

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:6
msgid "Editing messages"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí á n-eagarthóireacht"

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can edit messages and captions to file shares up to 6 hours after "
"sending."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat teachtaireachtaí agus fotheidil a chur in eagar le haghaidh "
"comhroinnte comhad suas le 6 huaire an chloig tar éis iad a sheoladh."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:14
msgid "Pinning messages"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí á bpriontáil"

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:16
msgid ""
"A moderator can pin important messages in a conversation, for a certain "
"period of time or until it's no longer relevant."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le modhnóir teachtaireachtaí tábhachtacha a phionáil i gcomhrá, ar"
" feadh tréimhse áirithe ama nó go dtí nach bhfuil sé ábhartha a thuilleadh."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:21
msgid ""
"Pinned messages are highlighted and accessible above the chat or in the "
"``Shared items`` tab of the content sidebar. If you no longer need a pinned "
"message, you can unpin it for everyone or only yourself from quick actions."
msgstr ""
"Tá teachtaireachtaí bioráilte aibhsithe agus inrochtana os cionn an chomhrá "
"nó sa chluaisín ``Míreanna Comhroinnte`` den bharra taoibh ábhair. Mura "
"bhfuil teachtaireacht bioráilte uait a thuilleadh, is féidir leat í a "
"dhíbhioráil do gach duine nó duit féin amháin ó ghníomhartha tapa."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:27
msgid "Setting reminder on messages"
msgstr "Meabhrúchán a shocrú ar theachtaireachtaí"

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:29
msgid ""
"You can set reminders on specific messages. If there's an important message "
"you want to be notified about later, simply hover over it and click on the "
"reminder icon."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat meabhrúcháin a shocrú ar theachtaireachtaí sonracha. Más ann "
"do theachtaireacht thábhachtach ar mhaith leat fógra a fháil fúithi níos "
"déanaí, níl le déanamh ach an luchóg a chur os a cionn agus cliceáil ar "
"dheilbhín an mheabhrúcháin."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:34
msgid ""
"In the submenu, you can select an appropriate time to receive a notification"
" later."
msgstr ""
"Sa fho-roghchlár, is féidir leat am oiriúnach a roghnú chun fógra a fháil "
"níos déanaí."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:42
msgid "Messages search in a conversation"
msgstr "Cuardach teachtaireachtaí i gcomhrá"

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:44
msgid ""
"In addition to global unified search, you can search for messages within a "
"specific conversation. In the content sidebar of a conversation, click the "
"search icon to open the search tab."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith le cuardach aontaithe domhanda, is féidir leat cuardach a "
"dhéanamh ar theachtaireachtaí laistigh de chomhrá ar leith. I mbarra taoibh "
"ábhair comhrá, cliceáil ar an deilbhín cuardaigh chun an cluaisín cuardaigh "
"a oscailt."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:49
msgid ""
"You can narrow down your search by using filters such as date range, and "
"sender."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do chuardach a chúngú trí scagairí amhail raon dáta agus "
"seoltóir a úsáid."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:55
msgid "Threaded messages"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí snáithithe"

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:57
msgid ""
"You can create threads in conversations to keep discussions organized. The "
"thread creation option is available in the new message additional actions."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat snáitheanna a chruthú i gcomhráite chun plé a choinneáil "
"eagraithe. Tá an rogha cruthú snáithe ar fáil sna gníomhartha breise "
"teachtaireachta nua."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:62
msgid ""
"Then, you can add a title and description for the thread and start the "
"discussion."
msgstr ""
"Ansin, is féidir leat teideal agus cur síos a chur leis an snáithe agus an "
"plé a thosú."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:67
msgid ""
"You can view all replies in a thread either from the replies button on the "
"message or from ``Shared items`` tab in the content sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat na freagraí go léir i snáithe a fheiceáil ón gcnaipe freagraí"
" ar an teachtaireacht nó ón táb ``Míreanna comhroinnte`` sa bharra taoibh "
"ábhair."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:72
msgid ""
"You can subscribe to a thread to receive notifications about new replies. It"
" is possible to subscribe from the thread itself or from the sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat liostáil le snáithe chun fógraí a fháil faoi fhreagraí nua. "
"Is féidir liostáil ón snáithe féin nó ón mbarra taoibh."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:77
msgid ""
"Subscribed threads are easily accessible from the navigation bar in "
"``Threads`` navigation."
msgstr ""
"Is furasta rochtain a fháil ar shnáitheanna suibscríofa ón mbarra "
"nascleanúna sa nascleanúint ``Snáitheanna``."

#: ../../talk/messages.rst:82
msgid ""
"You can edit the thread title from the thread itself or from the sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat teideal an snáithe a chur in eagar ón snáithe féin nó ón "
"mbarra taoibh."
